{
  "title": "Smoky Chewy Algerian Tomato Stir-fry",
  "description": "A brunch-friendly dish featuring a smoky and chewy texture made with tomatoes, onions, and aromatic herbs like bay leaves and thyme.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
